        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Vadimonium factum <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aio</ex></expan> Sulpicio <lb n="2"/>Fausto in VIII <expan><abbr>K</abbr><ex>alendas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ias</ex></expan> primas <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Put</abbr><ex>eolis</ex></expan> in foro ante aram <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Hord</abbr><ex>ionianam</ex></expan> hora tertia <lb n="5"/>HS D acturus ex <lb n="6"/>empto dari stipulatus <lb n="7"/>est <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Faenius Eume<lb break="no" n="8"/>nes spopondit <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Sulpi<lb break="no" n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">cius Faustus</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Tabula Pompeiana. (B): Geringe Leseabweichungen; Datierung: VIII K(alendas) Iul(ias) - nicht VIII N(onas) Iul(ias), wie Giordano und Landi meinen. (C): Die Tafel ist der Tabula Pompeiana 32 nicht ähnlich, sondern mit ihr identisch.</p>
            </div>
